(64688, 162876, 0, 1, '野人洞穴', '在追求夢想的過程途中，我們可能必須離開熟悉的地方，到一個全新的城市，在這之中可能會希望有一個人可以瞭解我們的夢想，雖然可能傻傻的，卻很美。\n堅定如腳步般的鋼琴，引領著如詩般的大提琴。野人的歌聲，就在山裡繞著，用陶淵明的詩句，唱出了夢想的烏托邦。\n你也有夢想嗎？聽聽這首歌吧，一首會讓夢想乘著歌聲飛翔的歌。專輯同名單曲，野性推薦', '2013-06-21 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 4, '野人洞穴　詞/曲 野人\n\n蓋上那大大的山葵葉\n鑽進這最刺人的包圍\n夢 還是那麼的甜 \n就算有眼淚 \n我不會後悔\n\n歡迎光臨野人的洞穴\n抱歉家徒四壁沒管弦\n笑 我早已與世隔絕\n無論魏晉 問你 今夕是何年\n\n還想要問 問你山下月光是否一樣\n星星有沒有比較亮\n也許會問 問妳是不是會選擇留下\n陪我在洞穴裡歌唱\n\n沿著花塢河岸向上追\n穿過雲霧寄居的界線\n是阿 這就是野人洞穴 \n阡陌荒會中 若隱若現\n\n別再要問 問我山路交縱何途是歸\n問山鳥何時會倦飛\n這就是我所謂 所謂的夢想 \n雖然傻傻 卻美的叫人狂\n\n【野人洞穴Facebook粉絲團】\nhttps://www.facebook.com/BCave.Music\n', '', 272, '', '野人', '野人', '', '野人', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-06-23 14:30:37', '2015-03-12 14:01:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(64689, 169633, 0, 1, 'Borderline', '走在被罪孽禁錮的煉獄邊緣\n看似崩潰的情緒卻無比清醒\n唯有你的愛才能讓一切重生', '2013-06-23 00:00:00', 2013, 19, 1, 1, 'Borderline 邊緣 / 詞曲: The Last Breath\n\n(A)\nYou''ve said you''re life''s fallin''\nYou wanna kill yourself\nCan I get the same of your courage?\nCuz waht I''ve only got is GUILT\n\nTell me WTF can I get after I''ve made it through?\nShould I commit by these: "You''re only suffering by those pills."?\n\n(B)\nWanna pull the trigger\nTo end my misery\n\nShow me what you believe\nThrilling with my voice\n\nIt''s outta control\nBleeding in the shadow\n\nWhere god has forsaken me\nPlease help me in here\n\n(C)\nFrom the very start, I was so convinced\nI''m about to touch the sky\nBut when I look back of my life\nThere''s only one step left of my borderline\n\nShould I stop right here or just take the leap?\nShould I just be who I am?\nI know this road is all alone\nBut I''m so tired to go, will you take me away?\n\n(Bridge)\nI am not the man you think\nCan''t take the pain behind my face\nBut I''ll try to fly, even my wings are far away from me.\nI know this is hard to believe\nBut it is everything to me\nEven most of you will leave this place\nI will still sing\n\nI WILL STILL SING!!\n\n(C)\nFrom the very start, I was so convinced\nI''m about to touch the sky\nBut when I look back of my life\nThere''s only one step left of my borderline\n\nI won''t stop right here or just take the brief\nI will just be who I am\nI know this wound is all alone\nBut I will let this go, so will you stay with me?', '', 279, '', 'The Last Breath', '威力', 'The Last Breath', 'The Last Breath', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-06-23 18:42:30', '2015-03-12 14:01:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(64690, 169633, 0, 1, 'Silver Rain', '描述一個痛失摯愛、人生接近毀滅邊緣的人\n他的內心世界與外在現實世界產生的扭曲', '2013-06-23 00:00:00', 2013, 19, 1, 1, 'The Last Breath - Silver Rain\n\n(A1)\nI wish that I was fine.\n我希望我能說自己過得很好\nBut there''s a scar left behind from my tears.\nStill can''t seize the days.\nWithout your breath, my whole life was a waste.\n\nDo you know I''m dying without you?\n\n(B)\nI find myself like an empty box.\nAnd trapping by the memories that fools me around.\n\n(C)\nDrown me in your eyes.\nLet me connect your soul inside.\nEven these silver rain will transfix me.\n\nDrown me in your eyes.\nPlease let me bear your pain.\nTake me away, or this silver rain will never ends.\n\n(A2)\nI wish that I was blind.\nThen I can cover my sight from these nightmares.\nWhy can''t I just end myself?\nThe hourglass stopped in the space you''re beating.\n\nDo you know I''m dying without you?\n\n(B)\nI find myself like an empty box.\nAnd trapping by the memories that fools me around.\n\n(C)\nDrown me in your eyes.\nLet me connect your soul inside.\nEven these silver rain will transfix me.\n\nDrown me in your eyes.\nPlease let me bear your pain.\nTake me away, or this silver rain will never ends.\n\n(間奏)\nI feel so alone.\nSince you were gone.\nMy world''s fallen apart.\n\n(C)\nDrown me in your eyes.\nLet me connect your soul inside.\nEven these silver rain will transfix me.\n\nDrown me in your eyes.\nPlease let me bear your pain.\nTake me away, or this silver rain will never ends.\n\nIt will never ends...', '', 273, '', 'The Last Breath', '威力', 'The Last Breath', 'The Last Breath', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-06-23 18:43:06', '2015-03-12 14:01:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
